    "title": "Can You Paint in Cold Weather? (Avoid The Trap)",
    "excerpt": "You slap the paint on, it feels dry to the touch, and you think you are in the clear. Three weeks later, it peels. Here is the reality of cold-weather painting.",
    "date": "2026-05-13",
